  <sect2>
    <title>Installation</title>

    <para>
      Install the package by running the following commands:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>./configure --localstatedir=/var/lib/locate \
            --disable-nls &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Now, as the <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem> user:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

    <sect3>
      <title>Command Explanations</title>

      <para>
        <parameter>--localstatedir=/var/lib/locate</parameter>: This switch
        changes the location of the <command>locate</command> database to be in
        <filename class="directory">/var/lib/locate</filename>, which is
        FHS-compliant.
      </para>

    </sect3>

